                <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/eca9805f-1d9d-4902-84d2-c15c7fa1aa27.sized-1000x1000.jpeg?w=50&amp;h=50&amp;auto=format&amp;mask=ellipse&amp;fit=facearea&amp;facepad=2.5" class="author-image float-left pr-2" />
